dball.com/wch/men/2015/match/2/008/Greece+-+Fyr+Macedonia Report]\n|goals1= [[Kiril Lazarov|Lazarov]] 10\n|goals2= [[Christo Tsatso|Tsatso]] 5\n|HT= 19\u20139\n|twomin1= 2\n|yellow1= 3\n|red1=\n|twomin2= 1\n|yellow2= 3\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Boris Trajkovski Sports Center]], [[Skopje]]\n|attendance= 6,963\n|referee= Hor\u00e1\u010dek, Novotn\u00fd\n|refnat= CZE\n}}\n''Macedonia won 62\u201348 on aggregate.''\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.eurohandball.com/wch/men/2015/round/3/Qualification+Europe Euro Handball]\n\n{{2015 World Men's Handball Championship qualification}}\n{{World Handball Championship}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2015 World Men's Handball Championship - European qualification}}\n[[Category:2013 in handball]]\n[[Category:2014 in handball]]\n[[Category:World Handball Championship tournaments]]\n[[Category:Qualification for handball competitions]]\n", "name_user": "Frietjes", "label": "safe", "comment": "expand templates perFb team TfD outcomeandFb competition TfD outcomeandFb cl TfD outcomeandFb rbr TfD outcome", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015_World_Men%27s_Handball_Championship_%E2%80%93_European_qualification"}
